register symbol for six reed basses.

To make it available,
@example
#(use-modules (scm accreg))
@end example
is required near the top of your input file.

This is primarily the register layout for the Hohner @qq{Gola} model.
The layout is

@lilypond[quote]
\\new PianoStaff
